OL,3,CDozens of firefighters tackling blaze
OL,4,Cat meat producer in Newtownards
OL,6,FFirefighters are tackling a large
OL,7,Fblaze at a meat producer in
OL,8,FNewtownards.
OL,10,FThe fire at Corries Meats on
OL,11,FCrossnamuckley Road was reported at
OL,12,F7.15pm on Saturday night, with dozens
OL,13,Fof firefighters at the site.
OL,15,FA Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,16,FService spokesperson said: "A large
OL,17,Ffire is ongoing at a number of sheds
OL,18,Fon the Crossnamuckley Road,
OL,19,FNewtownards.
OL,26,@xD@\OU
