CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776089466
OL,3,CDozens of firefighters tackling blaze
OL,4,Cat meat producer in Newtownards
OL,6,F"We currently have eight fire
OL,7,Fappliances, an aerial appliance, a
OL,8,Fwater tanker and a Command Support
OL,9,FUnit with 54 Firefighters in
OL,10,Fattendance.
OL,12,F"We request people to avoid the area
OL,13,Fto allow firefighting operations to
OL,14,Fcontinue."
OL,16,FA statement from the Corrie family
OL,17,Fthanked emergency services and said
OL,18,Feveryone was "safe and accounted for".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@JO]zD@NOUzD@eO]
