OL,3,CDozens of firefighters tackling blaze
OL,4,Cat meat producer in Newtownards
OL,6,FThey said: "Our family confirms a fire
OL,7,Fat one of our business properties; all
OL,8,Findividuals are safe and accounted for
OL,9,Fdespite the devastation caused.
OL,11,F"We thank emergency services and are
OL,12,Fworking with authorities while
OL,13,Fsupporting our people and operations."
OL,15,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson wrote on
OL,16,Fsocial media site X: "Thoughts and
OL,17,Fprayers this evening with everyone at
OL,18,FCorrie's farm.
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@AOUuD@fO]xD@VOU
