OL,3,CDozens of firefighters tackling blaze
OL,4,Cat meat producer in Newtownards
OL,6,F"Devastating news, and with wind
OL,7,Fconditions working against efforts to
OL,8,Fcontain it, the situation is
OL,9,Fincredibly difficult.
OL,11,F"Hoping for the safety of all involved
OL,12,Fand that the situation can be brought
OL,13,Funder control safely and swiftly."
